&lt;p&gt;This course will qualify those who successfully complete it to use the table saw, the jointer, and the thickness planer. It will comprise a one-hour classroom session covering the three tools with to respect to: tool specifications and features safety considerations selecting the appropriate tool for a given task correct and safe use of the tool The classroom session will be followed by a two to four-hour hands on session. During this session, using the tools will be demonstrated, with student use incorporated along with the demonstration. Part of this session will involve the student creating a small project from rough lumber.&lt;/p&gt;
